I"—<p>The Mobile App integration allows Open Peer Power mobile apps to easily integrate with Open Peer Power.</p>
<p>If you are planning to use a mobile application that integrates with Open Peer Power, we recommend that you keep this integration enabled.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>This integration is by default enabled, unless youâ€™ve disabled or removed the <a href="https://www.openpeerpower.io/integrations/default_config/"><code>default_config:</code></a> line from your configuration. If that is the case, the following example shows you how to enable this integration manually:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
mobile_app:</code></pre></figure>
